{"tid":2416762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點解四大唱片要跪 同返TVB和好？","createTime":"2021-02-21T10:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T19:00:59.000Z","uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f5de373a65b8ea6915cf1274bc78216645cee2a5","tid":2416762,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210221/4NNQQ33YZRG73OPKQXD5MUC6NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210221%2F4NNQQ33YZRG73OPKQXD5MUC6NQ%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ee0d9841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210221%2F4NNQQ33YZRG73OPKQXD5MUC6NQ%2F&h=204d4e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210221/4NNQQ33YZRG73OPKQXD5MUC6NQ/</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB人事變天，曾志偉踢走何哲圖掌管音樂事務，余詠珊被調離綜藝節目，志偉上任後的首要重大任務，就是要跟四大唱片重修舊好，事關大台自從跟四大反面後，近年勁歌金曲頒獎禮變星夢annual dinner，淪為笑柄，反而ViuTV不但綜藝節目《全民造星》做得有聲有色，成功捧紅姜濤和MIRROR多位成員，而且音樂節目《Chill Club》更贏盡行內和行外口碑，志偉要幫大台音樂節目救亡，惟有向四大唱片埋手，希望雙方破冰，而四大之中，擁有最多歌手的是環球唱片，日前環球接受《蘋果》訪問，坦言有合作機會，明幫志偉摑何哲圖和余詠珊一巴。<br />\n<br />\n⋯"},{"pid":"7897461d8c0b54339a9e8a191be1816382ff2bff","tid":2416762,"uid":52590,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死，咁d歌手做咩簽星夢"},{"pid":"3dc984795d293daac336e8037e48e229df6ba8c9","tid":2416762,"uid":292601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"都係錢姐"},{"pid":"dded534e0a867e512903a9248400c2cea86aacb5","tid":2416762,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":62,"score":-56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"和好都無用啦<br />\n<br />\n邊有人聽香港樂壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識樂理都叫自己做歌手<br />\n<br />\n係